              throws <A HREF="../../../../de/riwo/tetroid/tetris/IllegalFixRequestException.html" title="class in de.riwo.tetrix.tetris">IllegalFixRequestException</A></PRE>
<DL>
<DD>Takes over the given stone's allocation into this grid.
 
 Uses position and bounding box of the stone to determine
 which bricks are being allocated with the stone's color.
