 calls <A HREF="../../../../de/riwo/tetroid/tetris/Grid.html#notifyStoneFixListeners(de.riwo.tetrix.tetris.stone.Stone)"><CODE>notifyStoneFixListeners(Stone)</CODE></A>
 when the fix was successful.
<P>
<DD><DL>
<DT><B>Parameters:</B><DD><CODE>stone</CODE> - <A HREF="../../../../de/riwo/tetroid/tetris/stone/Stone.html" title="class in de.riwo.tetrix.tetris.stone"><CODE>Stone</CODE></A> to be fixed.
<DT><B>Throws:</B>
<DD><CODE><A HREF="../../../../de/riwo/tetroid/tetris/IllegalFixRequestException.html" title="class in de.riwo.tetrix.tetris">IllegalFixRequestException</A></CODE> - thrown when a brick
 demanded by the stone is not free</DL>
</DD>
</DL>
