<A NAME="clearLine(int)"><!-- --></A><H3>
clearLine</H3>
<PRE>
public boolean <B>clearLine</B>(int&nbsp;y)</PRE>
<DL>
<DD>Remove the bricks from this line and update the allocation.
 
 In more detail: the allocation of each line above the given
 line will be copied to the line below, i. e., all bricks
 above "fall" down one line
<P>
<DD><DL>
<DT><B>Parameters:</B><DD><CODE>y</CODE> - zero-based index of the line to be cleared
 (topmost line has index 0)
<DT><B>Returns:</B><DD>Whether the clearing was successful, i. e., if
 the given line was even full.</DL>
</DD>
</DL>
